NAME
  vcam::doc - Displays online documentation

SYNOPSIS
  vcam::doc()
  vcam::doc( func )

PARAMETER
  func - string, function name without the prefix "vcam::"

DESCRIPTION
  Displays a brief description of the module 'vcam', respectively the
  function vcam::'func'.

EXAMPLES
